        "source_sentence": "其親戚鄭逢原為予言之。",
        "translation": "A relative of his, Zheng Fengyuan, said this for him.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c25_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛像常有舍利",
        "translation": "\"Buddha images always have relics.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c26_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真州鍾離少師宅。",
        "translation": "Zhongli Shaoshi's house in Zhenzhou.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c27_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自任氏夫人修西方。",
        "translation": "Mrs. Ren cultivated the West.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c27_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雕阿彌陀佛像長四寸八分。",
        "translation": "She carved an image of Amitâbha Buddha four inches and eight minutes long.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c27_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "龕飾甚嚴。",
        "translation": "It's decorated with a very ornate niche.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c28_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常頂載行道。",
        "translation": "It always carries the image on its head as it travels along the path.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c28_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其像眉間常迸出舍利。",
        "translation": "Between his eyebrows, relics always burst out of his image.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c29_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大如黍米光彩照人出寶珠集。",
        "translation": "They were as big as millet and brilliant, and they produced a collection of precious pearls.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0277c29_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢佛遂得聰辯",
        "translation": "Dreaming of the Buddha, he then became wise and eloquent.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a02_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隋慧思禪師因夢阿彌陀佛與之說法。",
        "translation": "The Sui Chan master Huisi had a dream about Amitâbha Buddha and taught him the Dharma.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其後聰辯過人。",
        "translation": "Subsequently, he was exceedingly clever and eloquent.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a03_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "祥瑞不一。",
        "translation": "The auspicious rays were not uniform.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a04_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出往生傳。",
        "translation": "He went on to have a biography of rebirth in the Pure Land.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a04_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "念佛治病得愈",
        "translation": "He was cured of his illness by recitation of the Buddha's name.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "近年秀州一僧常念阿彌陀佛。",
        "translation": "In recent years, a monk in Xiuzhou always chanted Amitâbha Buddha.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a06_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為人治病。",
        "translation": "He treats people's illnesses.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a06_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有病者請往常得痊愈。",
        "translation": "Those who are sick often go there and are healed.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a06_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "秀州人皆能言之。",
        "translation": "Everyone in Xiuzhou could say.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a07_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "念佛孫兒免難",
        "translation": "'Mindful of the Buddha, our grandchildren will be spared trouble.'",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a08_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "予鄉村落間有一老人。",
        "translation": "\"There was an old man living in my village.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a09_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "每有事。",
        "translation": "Whenever there was something wrong, he would put his palms together and reach his forehead.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a09_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "必合掌至額。",
        "translation": "He would put his palms together and reach his forehead.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a09_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "念阿彌陀佛。",
        "translation": "He would chant Amitâbha Buddha.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a10_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其孫兒方二三歲。",
        "translation": "His grandson was two or three years old.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a10_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "因隨母至田野。",
        "translation": "He followed his mother to a field.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a10_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "忽失之。",
        "translation": "He suddenly lost him.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a11_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "老人尋訪不見。",
        "translation": "The old man searched for him and didn't see him.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a11_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後數日人告之云。",
        "translation": "A few days later, someone told him.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a11_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "在溪外。",
        "translation": "\"It's outside the stream.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a12_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "果尋得之。",
        "translation": "He found him.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a12_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見足跡。",
