        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a12_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遍於灘上。",
        "translation": "They were all over the beach.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a12_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其溪甚深。",
        "translation": "The stream was very deep.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a12_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知此兒何緣過。",
        "translation": "I don't know how this boy could have crossed it.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a13_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼又久而無恙。",
        "translation": "He hadn't been unharmed for a long time.",
        "source": "T47n1970_008:0278a13_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人以為其祖至誠阿彌陀佛所感也。",
        "translation": "People thought it was because his ancestor was so sincere about Amitâbha Buddha that he had been touched.",
